普罗米修斯火山(Prometheus)是[[木星|木星]]的[[卫星|卫星]]—[[木卫一|木卫一]]上的一座[[活火山|活火山]]，它位于面向木星半球的南纬1.52度，西经153.94度处<ref name=Featurenames>{{cite web | last=Blue | first=Jennifer | date=October 1, 2008 | url=http://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/jsp/FeatureTypesData2.jsp?systemID=5&bodyID=7&typeID=11&system=Jupiter&body=Io&type=Eruptive%20center&sort=AName&show=Fname&show=Lat&show=Long&show=Diam&show=Stat&show=Orig | title=Io Nomenclature: Eruptive center | publisher=USGS | accessdate=2008-10-01 | archive-date=2006-10-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061002022255/http://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/jsp/FeatureTypesData2.jsp?systemID=5&bodyID=7&typeID=11&system=Jupiter&body=Io&type=Eruptive%20center&sort=AName&show=Fname&show=Lat&show=Long&show=Diam&show=Stat&show=Orig | dead-url=no }}</ref>。 
 
 

==描述==
普罗米修斯火山是由一座28公里（17英里）宽的普罗米修斯火山口和一条100公里（62英里）长的混合[[熔岩流|熔岩流]]所构成，环四周覆盖着微红的[[硫|硫磺]]和圆形、发亮的[[二氧化硫|二氧化硫]]火山喷发物<ref name="IoVolcanismChap12">{{cite book |last=Davies |first=A. |title=Volcanism on Io: A Comparison with Earth |year=2007 |publisher=[[Cambridge_University_Press|Cambridge University Press]] |isbn=978-0-521-85003-2 |pages=208–216 |chapter=Prometheus and Amirani: effusive activity and insulated flows }}</ref>。1979年3月，从[[旅行者1号|旅行者1号]]探测器拍摄的照片中首次观测到了该火山<ref name="Smith1979">{{cite journal |title=The Jupiter system through the eyes of Voyager 1 |journal=Science |last=Smith |first=B. A. |display-authors=etal  |pages=951–972 |volume=204 |issue= 4396|year=1979 |doi=10.1126/science.204.4396.951 |pmid=17800430 |bibcode=1979Sci...204..951S|s2cid=33147728 }}</ref>，同年稍晚，[[国际天文联合会|国际天文联合会]]以[[希腊|希腊]]火神[[普罗米修斯|普罗米修斯]]之名命名了该特征。 

普罗米修斯为一处火山喷发点，自与1979年旅行者1号交会以来，该火山一直在持续喷发。在与旅行者1号交会和伽利略号探测器首次观测之间，又形成了一块6700平方公里（2600平方英里）的熔岩流场<ref name="McEwen1998a">{{cite journal |title=Active Volcanism on Io as Seen by Galileo SSI |journal=Icarus |last=McEwen |first=A. S. |display-authors=etal  |pages=181–219 |volume=135 |issue= 1|year=1998| doi = 10.1006/icar.1998.5972 | bibcode = 1998Icar..135..181M}}</ref>。后来伽利略探测器对该熔岩流场的观测显示出许多小的断裂处，尤其是在熔岩流场的西端<ref name="Keszthelyi2001">{{cite journal |title=Imaging of volcanic activity on Jupiter's moon Io by Galileo during the Galileo Europa Mission and the Galileo Millennium Mission |journal=J. Geophys. Res. |last=Keszthelyi |first=L. |display-authors=etal  |pages=33025–33052 |volume=106 |issue= E12|year=2001 |doi=10.1029/2000JE001383|bibcode = 2001JGR...10633025K }}</ref>。
 

普罗米修斯火山是两道火山喷发束流的源头地：一束较小、富[[硫|硫]]的喷流源自熔岩流场东端的岩浆源喷孔；另一束高达75到100公里（47到62英里）、富含[[二氧化硫|二氧化硫]]尘埃的喷流柱是从另一端活跃的岩浆流锋所喷发出来的<ref name="IoVolcanismChap12"/>。前者在普罗米修斯熔岩流场东面形成了一片弥散的红色沉积区，而后者环整个火山和熔岩流周边形成一片明亮的圆形沉积区。富含二氧化硫的喷流是覆盖在熔岩流场西端的二氧化硫霜因受热蒸发而成<ref name="Kieffer 2000">{{cite journal |title=Prometheus: Io's Wandering Plume |journal=Science |last=Kieffer |first=S.W. |display-authors = etal |pages=1204–1208 |volume=288 |issue=5469 |year=2000 |doi=10.1126/science.288.5469.1204|pmid=10817989 |bibcode =   2000Sci...288.1204K}}</ref>，是多个断裂处产生的气体和尘埃混合而成的可见尘埃喷流<ref name="Milazzo2001">{{cite journal |title=Observations and initial modeling of lava-{{Chem|SO|2}} interactions at Prometheus, Io |journal=J. Geophys. Res. |last=Milazzo |first=M. P. |display-authors=etal  |pages=33121–33128 |volume=106 |issue= E12|year=2001 |doi=10.1029/2000JE001410|bibcode = 2001JGR...10633121M }}</ref>。[[旅行者1号|旅行者1号]]、 [[伽利略号探测器|伽利略号]]和[[新视野号|新视野号]]在每次恰当的拍摄时机都观测到了普罗米修斯的喷发流束。
 

